Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.47,0:00:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.34,0:00:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.54,0:00:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.28,0:00:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.03,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動了 諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題!\N可是 琉菜還沒到耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來那傢伙還不是逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜現在人在到沖繩去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天對她來講\N是個重要的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.66,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的日子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沖繩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.73,0:02:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩是琉菜小姐的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我的想法\N我覺得她是去約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦!約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要不要和我試試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑般的表情\N留在你臉上就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司是開玩笑的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真的相信啊!真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會隨後再加以通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能先到現場待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七話 沙灘上的重鑽少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人 妳是沖繩人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳給人感覺就是本地人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回老家的感覺很不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...妳是第一次看到那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做國際和平中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.33,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好像還有以戰爭及和平\N為主題的博物館跟美術館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是舉辦國際和平會議的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.64,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯那是為了舉行會議\N而特別建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.65,0:03:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過當地人\N倒不怎麼認同就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來司機先生也不怎麼高興耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.89,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高層的人很希望\N在這個島上舉行會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才討厭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在會議桌上講得天花亂墜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果什麼也不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是...\N琉菜父親的忌日...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有她父親的話\N我們根本無法把初戰打的如此漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.73,0:04:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我在跟外星異種作戰喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會好好保衛\N爸爸深愛著的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~哎呀~這不是琉菜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.78,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛剛掃完爸爸的墓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊今天是阿鯨的忌日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.66,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~哎呀~真虧妳沒忘記\N還特地跑回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿鯨他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個工作狂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是發生事故吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難為妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了!今天就住我這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!可是我沒那麼多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得馬上趕回去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?當天來回呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣說嘛 就住下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惠理香她啊 都結婚了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這、這、這是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G...重鑽機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...琉菜小姐...那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G要塞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家全來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡果然超級熱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.48,0:07:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好舒暢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司下水吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好看好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我華麗的跳水姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可跟斗牙的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是身經百戰的...\N好啦好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 斗牙\N穿泳裝來是正確的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還相當暴露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不關我的事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說"休閒活動也是必要的"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是桑德曼說的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別怪我多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也幫您準備好了泳裝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這應該不是我的喜好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換掉啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是怎麼弄的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...來玩就來玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛還開著超重機組過來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是桑德曼的指示啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是琉菜小姐\N沒一起搭乘的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我一個人去控制G重鑽機\N我實在有點沒信心耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔!是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露是第一次來沖繩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我出生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳能喜歡就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過過去五次神秘敵人\N外星異種的來襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.78,0:09:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界陷入了空前的混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不談政治經濟面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光就民間階層來講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外星異種的出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.56,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而造成社會中多方面的恐慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我在此重申
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值此混沌不清之際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也正是發揮我地球聯合政府\N真正價值的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哀怨現況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.97,0:10:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位代表應更加努力\N來保障民眾的安全...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從地底而來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統請快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星...異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統請快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是超漂亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也潛下去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再不抹防曬油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你肯定會哭死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人這樣才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.56,0:11:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G呼叫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些個外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧!我就說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.52,0:12:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛跑到人家家裡胡鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及所有超重機組都啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有座艙影像顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!好誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個... 想這樣去作戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 這是緊急狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣也有其特別的美感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 請聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受害範圍\N很可能會波及整個沖繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為和平會議之故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的沖繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現暫時性的\N人口密度過高現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求大量殺戮的外星異種\N就是為此而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國際和平中心的襲擊\N只不過是個開端而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你、你在喊什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想跟著一起喊看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 根本看不到外星異種嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是逃走了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還在!應該還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜!冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道!因為這是我的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要保護啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.13,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重破壞砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有效...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種潛到地下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.82,0:16:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推測外星異種應該是靠\N地面的聲音反應作出攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是說降落地面的途中\N就成了牠的飼料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?不下去的話\N就根本動不了牠啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用G重鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從地底把牠轟出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後大家集中攻擊那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學分解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜!螢幕就請妳盯著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從左邊快速朝向這邊移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個緊急事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA決定出動超重神...\N加油!超『澎』神..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是超重神啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你呀?回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正誘導外星異種上升至地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通告超重皇\N以及超重機組全體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體準備攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為擔心特地跑回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒聽到避難廣播嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險!快點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超『澎』神...\N超重神.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行不通!沒有效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是牠的防衛太完美了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下!琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那招在模擬訓練時\N從來都沒有成功過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功率還不到百分之五呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止攻擊都沒有效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用超重鑽\N要是用超重鑽的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以對牠造成損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果集中於一點給予\N超過牠負載量的打擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好就能穿透那個裝甲是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.72,0:18:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左側重鑽機\N超重壓力拳發射預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔哇!超重鑽真是酷斃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊!超澎神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說是超重神了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.74,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在您的故鄉上\N這麼胡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想開重鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我交換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不~~行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真的很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座島真的很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠守護住這裡\N我也很高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好!斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位!休假玩得還愉快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑、桑德曼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 出發吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位 隨我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的浪花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要衝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.47,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人被留下來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.79,0:21:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.13,0:21:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.18,0:22:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.66,0:22:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.73,0:22:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.33,0:22:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.04,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.07,0:22:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.18,0:22:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.62,0:22:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.39,0:22:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.27,0:22:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種居然侵入城內了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在超重皇正在應戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?駕駛者是英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.11,0:22:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出\N"超重戰場"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.87,0:23:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週 也將照料各位的和平!